**Approved Project:** “Approved Project” means the industrial project of an enterprise/ an expansion project in the manufacturing sector which should be approved before implementation of the project by any Directorate under the Deptt. of Micro, Small &amp;amp; Medium Enterprises and Textiles, Govt. of West Bengal or concerned DIC or Micro, Small &amp;amp; Medium Enterprises Development Institute (MSMEDI), Govt. of India or Food Processing Industries &amp;amp; Horticulture Deptt., Govt. of West Bengal or Commercial Banks/ Financial Institution (Central and State)/ Cooperative Banks/ scheduled banks approved byCentral RBI/ RRBs financing the project.
